
If you are implimenting end 2 end project
1. start backend > npm start 
2. state react > npm start 

Backend NodeJS Project

> npm init -y
  updating package.json
  "start" :"nodemon app.js"
  
> npm i express bcryptjs jsonwebtoken dotenv mongoose morgan chalk 


Frontend 
>npx create-react-app client 
cd client
npm start 

--------------------------------
What we required in React?

1.SPA             - React-router-dom
2.State Managment - redux,react-redux redux-devtools-extension 

Install required Packages 
client>npm i react-router-dom redux react-redux  redux-devtools-extension



